    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/bittersweet/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1029137-18.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bittersweet/" class="author">
